# AI Engineering from Scratch — API Keys
# ========================================
# This project uses opencode as its AI agent.
# Configure your provider via:
#   opencode  ->  /connect
# Or set your keys directly:
#
# OpenCode Zen (recommended):
#   Get your key at https://opencode.ai/auth
#   Then:  opencode  ->  /connect  ->  OpenCode Zen
#
# For the API call examples in this lesson:
#   OPENCODE_API_KEY=oc_zen_...
#
# The actual LLM calls go through opencode's provider.
# OpenCode supports 75+ providers — see https://opencode.ai/docs/providers
